OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784359131
OL,3,CTeenager accused of stabbing teacher
OL,4,Cbecause she was an 'easy target'
OL,6,FA teenage boy accused of stabbing his
OL,7,Fteacher in the head allegedly did so
OL,8,Fbecause she was "an easy target" as a
OL,9,F"lone young female".
OL,11,FThe 16-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,12,Ffor legal reasons, has pleaded not
OL,13,Fguilty to attempted murder, after the
OL,14,Fincident at Milford Haven
OL,15,FComprehensive School in February of
OL,16,Fthis year.
OL,18,FChristopher Rees KC, acting on behalf
OL,19,Fof the prosecution, argued that the
OL,20,Fteenager carried out a "calculated and
OL,21,Fplanned attack" on Vicki Williams.
OL,26,@|D@XOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
