OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784359131
OL,3,CTeenager accused of stabbing teacher
OL,4,Cbecause she was an 'easy target'
OL,6,FThe prosecution later told the jury
OL,7,Fthat the defendant had decided not to
OL,8,Ftell anyone else in the school that he
OL,9,Fwas in possession of the knife that
OL,10,Fday.
OL,12,FThey said: "If he'd told anyone else,
OL,13,Fhe could have been stopped, so he kept
OL,14,Fit his secret."
OL,16,FIn his closing speech, Mr Rees KC put
OL,17,Fto the jury: "Why Vicki Williams?
OL,18,FWell, she was, at quarter past three,
OL,19,Fa lone female teacher, she was an easy
OL,20,Ftarget.
OL,26,@tD@LOUvD@OO]yD@NOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784359131
OL,3,CTeenager accused of stabbing teacher
OL,4,Cbecause she was an 'easy target'
OL,6,F"He's not attacked a male teacher, has
OL,7,Fhe? He's attacked one of the young,
OL,8,Ffemale teachers, alone in her
OL,9,Fclassroom."
OL,11,F"It is only because he struck the back
OL,12,Fof her skull, and she fought back,
OL,13,Fthat she is here to tell you," he
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,FThe court previously heard the boy
OL,17,Fapproached her desk on the afternoon
OL,18,Fof February 5 this year to ask her to
OL,19,Fcheck his work.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
