PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784359131
OL,3,CTeenager accused of stabbing teacher
OL,4,Cbecause she was an 'easy target'
OL,6,FIt was when he shut the door to the
OL,7,Fclassroom, saying it was cold, that
OL,8,F"alarm bells" began to ring in her
OL,9,Fhead.
OL,11,FThe jury was told the student then
OL,12,Fpulled a large kitchen knife from his
OL,13,Fbag, allegedly striking her in the
OL,14,Fhead.
OL,16,FThe court previously heard a "violent
OL,17,Fstruggle" ensued in which Mrs Williams
OL,18,Ftried to take the knife from him
OL,19,Fbefore he ran from the school.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]xD@^OUyD@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
