FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784359131
OL,3,CTeenager accused of stabbing teacher
OL,4,Cbecause she was an 'easy target'
OL,6,FThe defence put it to the jury that
OL,7,Fthe defendant brought a knife into
OL,8,Fschool to show off to his group of
OL,9,Ffriends.
OL,11,FMatthew Roberts KC, defending, said
OL,12,Fthe teenager was someone with no prior
OL,13,Fhistory of violence.
OL,15,FThe defence argued: "There's no
OL,16,Fevidence of any prior animosity or ill
OL,17,Ffeeling between them at all. He, we
OL,18,Fsay, had no reason to want to hurt
OL,19,FVicki Williams.
OL,26,@wD@UOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784359131
OL,3,CTeenager accused of stabbing teacher
OL,4,Cbecause she was an 'easy target'
OL,6,F"We cannot be sure his actions were
OL,7,Fdeliberate."
OL,9,FOn Friday 17 July, Judge Paul Thomas
OL,10,FKC later summarised all evidence the
OL,11,Fcourt has heard over the past
OL,12,Ffortnight, before adjourning
OL,13,Fproceedings for the day.
OL,15,FThe court has previously heard Mrs
OL,16,FWilliams attended Withybush Hospital
OL,17,Fto be treated for a wound she had
OL,18,Fsustained to her scalp, scratches on
OL,19,Fher back and minor cuts to her hands.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@LO]
