CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784359131
OL,3,CTeenager accused of stabbing teacher
OL,4,Cbecause she was an 'easy target'
OL,6,FThe defendant has pleaded not guilty
OL,7,Fto attempted murder, wounding with
OL,8,Fintent to cause grievous bodily harm
OL,9,Fand unlawful wounding. The trial
OL,10,Fcontinues at Swansea Crown Court.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/7
